Slope

A fantastic speed run game, Slope Game lets you roll a ball down slopes and obstacles. Try your luck on this endless course and see how far you can get.

The goal of this running game is to drive the ball as far as possible to get the highest score possible. The game features a simple control system and fast-paced gameplay. Start playing the game by pressing the arrow keys on your keyboard. You must control the ball rolling through the course while it is sloped and has red obstacles.

If you keep the ball on the course for a longer period of time, it will roll faster. You will find this game to be both exhilarating and challenging at the same time. The ball can be practiced hundreds of times without colliding with obstacles while continuing down the slope. If you enjoy fast-paced platform games, this game will be right up your alley.
